Titolo: Bugsnax

Anno: 2020

Descrizione: Bugsnax is an adventure video game developed by independent game studio Young Horses. In the game, players explore a mysterious island and attempt to find and capture the eponymous half-bug-half-snack creatures. The game was unveiled via an announcement trailer shown during Sony's PlayStation 5 live-streamed reveal event on June 11, 2020. British indie pop band Kero Kero Bonito performed the game's theme song, which was featured in the announcement trailer. The game was released on November 12, 2020 for the PlayStation 5, PlayStation 4, Microsoft Windows, and macOS. An expansion pack, Bugsnax: The Isle of Bigsnax was announced on October 27, 2021 and will release in the first quarter of 2022.